{"tid":99794,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"2017DSE 中文科一齊最後衝刺","createTime":"2017-01-29T12:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T15:19:08.000Z","uid":69157,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe7eb7c92d00dafa6b06f04aacac813207f63ab","tid":99794,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T12:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家準備成點？<br />\n<br />\n我分享下少少唔同卷嘅部署<br />\n<br />\n=======閱讀=======<br />\nCE 07~11 <br />\nDSE pp 12~16 <br />\n文言ce 90~05<br />\n<br />\n溫常用文言用字<br />\n唔使刻意操文言<br />\n摸熟dse marking 先 <br />\n<br />\n=======作文=======<br />\n每星期作一篇非擅長文體兩篇擅長文體（求5以上）<br />\n作一篇文（基本）<br />\n<br />\n開始砌屬於自己嘅框架<br />\n堆好要用嘅字句 at least 背&gt;50 個 句&gt;20句<br />\n<br />\n=======聆聽=======<br />\n先摸熟ce 07~11<br />\n再集中做dse pp 12~15<br />\n再昇華溫al 聆聽 <br />\n最後先做16 同 mock 務求操到10題全對<br />\n慳時間就反覆操dse 就ok<br />\n<br />\n=======綜合=======<br />\n了解返四柱評分<br />\n背好各種格式<br />\n公私函各背一種上下款就夠<br />\n每種格式用字用句要熟 非常熟 <br />\n特別頭尾句點砌 砌好每種文體既頭尾句<br />\n溫熟每年pp 點考你語境<br />\n執靚自己用字 每篇文體都要有一篇自己寫出黎嘅範文<br />\n<br />\n=======說話=======<br />\n了解評分方法<br />\n練 練 練！<br />\n溫好唔同題型 搵晒 keywords examples 陰人位<br />\n一定會翻炒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 懶 打住咁多先 <br />\n一齊加油"},{"pid":"2bb95431c98be7ccb76698dc22834d86b1eed2f4","tid":99794,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cc7a580e7e70d9b8ccdf3307c002c8af88ed2b","tid":99794,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:09:45.000Z","msg":"洗乜溫<br />\n2017DSE各科試卷流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/96076/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/96076/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n有晒題目"},{"pid":"7c157141da85721