從入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問"},{"pid":"ba0ca33af1994d44b96d5885007ad6b1aa27ce4a","tid":99794,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲未開始溫 唔知點入手溫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇餸食飯<br />\n自己最差邊份卷 溫左先 <br />\n平靚正既話 綜合&gt;聆聽&gt;說話&gt;閱讀&gt;寫作"},{"pid":"2cfa75d082bb3ccbaea08495295e4d2630d04ab6","tid":99794,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c576399f005811c73ae8252f674030b323f8872a","tid":99794,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:28:38.000Z","msg":"完全放棄文言文<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93435b044a1cf9fcf2777b5421ca35a2394ecac","tid":99794,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你好 請問一下 關於卷一段落大意<br />\n我次次都係分啱曬段 但寫唔中段落大意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問有咩方法可以改善？或者應該點溫？<br />\n依家無從入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問</blockquote><br />\n分岩段證明你語感不俗<br />\n但表達書寫能力差<br />\n試下每次你分岩段既原因係原文圈出黎<br />\n由原文湊合關鍵字 組成基本答案<br />\n再加入段落對結構 文意有咩影響<br />\n如：從1,2,3段你都搵到講小學既回憶<br />\n文本就係 (動詞根據文體）+小學回憶<br />\n對文意影響就係表達作者對。。。。之情<br />\n或帶咩哲理<br />\n或者<br />\n係做承上啟下/ 正反對比等<br />\n視乎段落變化"},{"pid":"1ddb74f7690779e08780b959dac10130bc66a422","tid":99794,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全放棄文言文<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同意咁做<br />\n記熟常用字 做足90~05文言短文就夠"},{"pid":"0971e42f36e503c39c795c8592380898258a7ca0","tid":99794,"uid":80329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:34:25.000Z","msg":"作文作咩文體易d高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 中文廢渣"},{"pid":"a617aea1477287174a2805a2f161cdaa37ce3439","tid":99794,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:39:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>作文作咩文體易d高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 中文廢渣</blockquote><br />\n如果議論文係中產政府工<br />\n記敘文就係創業<br />\n講咩自己諗"},{"pid":"eb2ed5ac6f9e757b72ceec43b6dc5d6c11c8b870","tid":99794,"uid":71000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:44:51.000Z","msg":"溫中文真係on99 平時學校幫你操已經夠<br />\n你自己點溫都冇用 完全睇彩數<br />\n真心講 aim3/4咪撚溫啦 曬時間<br />\nAim5or above果班，你本身有冇咁嘅能力？<br />\n課堂作文係咪次次都佳作？<br />\n至少我識以前果班5**果班人 係每一次份份卷都顯示出佢係有咁嘅能力<br />\n本身3/4果班點操都操唔到<br />\n放時間係有信心科啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158537910f9cb14fc21126b11468e7c2d56bc5a7","tid":99794,"uid":28941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>溫中文真係on99 平時學校幫你操已經夠<br />\n你自己點溫都冇用 完全睇彩數<br />\n真心講 aim3/4咪撚溫啦 曬時間<br />\nAim5or above果班，你本身有冇咁嘅能力？<br />\n課堂作文係咪次次都佳作？<br />\n至少我識以前果班5**果班人 係每一次份份卷都顯示出佢係有咁嘅能力<br />\n本身3/4果班點操都操唔到<br />\n放時間係有信心科啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擺多d時間投資其他科著數d"}]}